夏奇拉的作品融合了多种风格。其中包括民俗、主流流行(mainstream pop)和[[电子音乐|电音]]。在《Rolling Stone》的一次采访中，夏奇拉说：“我的音乐，我觉得吧，是多种不同类型元素的混合品。我总是在进行新的试验。所以我试图去使自己不被固定的风格所束缚，也不想把自己被划入固定不变的类别中，或者呢... (不如说是不想)作茧自缚。”<ref>{{cite web |last=Mim |first=Udovitch |url=http://www.rollingstone.com/artists/shakira/articles/story/5931811/qa_shakira |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090207181309/http://www.rollingstone.com/artists/shakira/articles/story/5931811/qa_shakira |archivedate=2009-02-07 |title=Q&A: Shakira – A pop artist with a rock & roll heart |publisher=Rollingstone |accessdate=November 27, 2009 |date=January 23, 2002 |quote="My music, I think, is a fusion of many different elements. And I'm always experimenting. So I try not to limit myself, or put myself in a category, or... be the architect of my own jail." |deadurl=yes }}</ref>她早期的西班牙语专辑（如《赤足》和《小偷在哪里？》）都属于民俗音乐和拉美流行风格的混合品。而她的英语专辑（如《爱情洗礼》）则受[[流行摇滚|流行摇滚]]和{{link-en|拉丁流行|pop Latino}}的影响较大。<ref>{{cite web |last=Lechner |first=Ernesto |url=http://www.rollingstone.com/artists/shakira/albums/album/314397/review/5941112/laundry_service |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090626070950/http://www.rollingstone.com/artists/shakira/albums/album/314397/review/5941112/laundry_service |archivedate=2009-06-26 |date=October 17, 2001 |title=Shakira: Laundry Service Review |publisher=Rollingstone |accessdate=November 27, 2009 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>《爱情洗礼》以流行音乐风格为主，但也兼有一些风格多元化的味道。<ref name=backgroundtitlebillboard>{{cite book|last=Cobo|first=Leila|title=Billboard|publisher=[[尼爾森NV|尼爾森NV]]|page=94|url=http://books.google.com/?id=ABIEAAAAMBAJ&pg=PA94&dq=the+reason+I+named+it+Laundry+Service+is+because+I've+spent+the+year+dedicated+to+my+two+great+passions#v=onepage&q=the%20reason%20I%20named%20it%20Laundry%20Service%20is%20because%20I've%20spent%20the%20year%20dedicated%20to%20my%20two%20great%20passions&f=false|accessdate=November 10, 2013|date=November 10, 2001|issn=0006-2510|volume=113|issue=45}}</ref>夏奇拉将这些特点归因于其血统的复杂性，说“我是混血人。混搭是我的天性。我是白种与黑种人的混合品、流行和摇滚的混合品以及不同文化的混合品——(这些特性分别来自于)黎巴嫩国籍的父亲、西班牙血统的母亲、哥伦比亚民俗文化、我喜爱的阿拉伯舞蹈和美洲音乐。”<ref name=shakiinterviewfaze>{{cite web|last=Ma|first=Suzanne|title=Cover Story: Shakira - A Cultural Fusion|url=http://www.faze.ca/issue07/shakira.html|work={{link-en|Faze|Faze (magazine)}}|accessdate=November 10, 2013|quote="I am a fusion. That's my persona. I'm a fusion between black and white, between pop and rock, between cultures - between my Lebanese father and my mother's Spanish blood, the Colombian folklore and Arab dance I love and American music."|archive-date=2014-09-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140907120827/http://www.faze.ca/issue07/shakira.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>[[阿拉伯音乐|阿拉伯音乐]]和中东元素的影响在专辑《小偷在哪里？》<ref name=shakiinterviewfaze />和《爱情洗礼》中都有较多体现，尤其是歌曲《如你这般眼神》(Ojos Así)。<ref name=reviewallmusic>{{cite web|last=Henderson|first=Alex|title=Laundry Service - Shakira|url=http://www.allmusic.com/album/laundry-service-mw0000016418|publisher=AllMusic. Rovi Corporation|accessdate=November 10, 2013|archive-date=2015-07-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150713055004/http://www.allmusic.com/album/laundry-service-mw0000016418|dead-url=no}}</ref>这些专辑还融入了源自南美多国的不同元素。例如在歌曲《拒斥》("Objection")中，就能见到源于[[阿根廷|阿根廷]]的快节奏音乐风格{{link-en|探戈 (音乐)|Tango (music)|探戈}}与[[摇滚|摇滚]]元素的组合。<ref name=backgroundtitlebillboard />在激速音乐(uptempo)搭配吉他独奏的同时，更穿插有夏奇拉[[饶舌|饶舌]]式的唱腔。<ref name=reviewguardian>{{cite web|last=Petridis|first=Alexis|title=Thong songs|url=http://www.theguardian.com/music/2002/mar/08/popandrock.shopping|work=[[卫报|卫报]]|publisher=卫报媒体集团|accessdate=November 10, 2013|date=March 8, 2002|archive-date=2015-07-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150708131617/http://www.theguardian.com/music/2002/mar/08/popandrock.shopping|dead-url=no}}</ref>

《女狼出没》以[[电子音乐|电子音乐]]风格为主，同时也吸收了非洲、哥伦比亚、印度和中东等多地的音乐元素。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/267379/shakira-the-she-wolf-billboard-cover-story|title=Shakira: The 'She Wolf' Billboard Cover Story|work=Billboard|accessdate=November 27, 2009|archive-date=2013-02-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130202075307/http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/956430/katy-perry-tops-songs-of-the-summer-2010-chart|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last=Ditzian |first=Eric |url=http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1616583/shakira-new-album-very-electronic.jhtml |title=Shakira Says New Album She Wolf Is 'Very Electronic' |publisher=MTV.com |date=2009-07-21 |accessdate=2014-03-24 |archive-date=2013-12-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131217221637/http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1616583/shakira-new-album-very-electronic.jhtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>夏奇拉称这张专辑就像是一次“乐音试验之旅”，还表示自己为了“把电子音乐和世界万籁、[[铃鼓|铃鼓]]、[[单簧管|单簧管]]、{{link-en|东方音乐|Music of Asia}}、[[印度音乐|印度音乐]]和{{link-en|舞厅乐 (牙买加)|Dancehall|牙买加舞厅乐}}都组合到一起”，曾研究和比较过许多国家的[[民俗音乐|民俗音乐]]。<ref name=albumpageshakira.com>{{cite web |title=She Wolf |url=http://archive.shakira.com/discography/index/album/albumId/21/tagName/Albums |publisher=Shakira.com (Archive) |accessdate=September 28, 2013 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121109221440/http://archive.shakira.com/discography/index/album/albumId/21/tagName/Albums |archivedate=2012-11-09 }}</ref>2010年专辑《日出》则是对最初风格的一次回归。这张专辑收录有民谣如《无比重要》("Lo Que Más")和《6点以前》("Antes de las Seis")，摇滚歌曲如《你的嘴(唇)》("Tu Boca")和《热情忘我》("Devoción")，以及拉美舞曲如《痴狂》("Loca")。<ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/music/shakira-plans-november-release-for-sale-el-sol-2060107.html | location=London | work=The Independent | title=Shakira plans November release for 'Sale El Sol' | date=August 23, 2010 | accessdate=2015-04-18 | archive-date=2010-09-24 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100924061724/http://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/music/shakira-plans-november-release-for-sale-el-sol-2060107.html | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.sonymusic.de/Shakira/Sale-El-Sol/P/2428016 |title=Shakira – Sale El Sol – Sony Music Entertainment Germany GmbH |publisher=Sonymusic.de |accessdate=October 22, 2010 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20101011023557/http://www.sonymusic.de/Shakira/Sale-El-Sol/P/2428016 |archivedate=2010-10-11 }}</ref>

夏奇拉舞技出众，在《難以抗拒》和《女狼現身》等多個MV中展現出较高的身體柔韧度。夏奇拉於2009年歌曲《Give It Up To Me》的MV中，有一段是夏奇拉[[化身|化身]][[千手觀音|千手觀音]]於[[香港|香港]]的[[維多利亞港|維多利亞港]]熱舞。

